N2  - The article presents an update on issues related to management as of September 1966. Several books about corporate management have been named winners of the 1965 McKinsey Foundation-Academy of Management Book Awards. The 10th annual meeting of the Midwest Division of the Academy of Management will be held at Northwestern University on April 7 and 8, 1967. Joseph A. Litterer received the eighth annual Organization Development Council Publications Award for his book ?Analysis of Organizations.?
